OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780665075
OL,3,CMan shot with crossbow at University
OL,4,Cof Surrey
OL,6,FA man in his 50s is in a serious
OL,7,Fcondition in hospital after being shot
OL,8,Fwith a crossbow at Manor Park Student
OL,9,FVillage, Guildford, at around 10am
OL,10,Fthis morning (4 June).
OL,12,FSurrey Police say a 21-year-old Saudi
OL,13,Fnational, who was a former student at
OL,14,Fthe university, has been arrested on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of attempted murder and is
OL,16,Fcurrently in custody.
OL,18,FA significant emergency services
OL,19,Fpresence remains in place. Access to
OL,20,Fthe Royal Surrey County Hospital is
OL,21,Funaffected.
