OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780665075
OL,3,CMan shot with crossbow at University
OL,4,Cof Surrey
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Jon Groenen said:
OL,7,F"I appreciate that this incident will
OL,8,Fcause concern amongst our local
OL,9,Fcommunities, and I can reassure that
OL,10,Fwe are not looking for anyone else in
OL,11,Frelation to this incident. We are
OL,12,Fworking closely with the university as
OL,13,Four investigation progresses.
OL,15,F"The suspect was detained at the scene
OL,16,Fshortly after the incident and an
OL,17,Finvestigation is now underway to
OL,18,Festablish the circumstances of the
OL,19,Fassault."
